  "governance_notes": "PlaceOrder and CancelOrder are atomic operations requiring rollback capability. ParseCommand and TrackOrder are pure functions with no side effects. All children's global_vars are subsets of parent's global_vars. No child introduces new data stores beyond those declared by parent."
